headline.main: Inbee Park Wins LPGA Singapore by 1 Stroke With Closing 64
headline.print_headline: Inbee Park Wins LPGA Singapore by 1 Stroke With Closing 64

lead_paragraph: Inbee Park used her self-described "amazing" putting to win the HSBC Women's Champions tournament by one stroke on Sunday after closing with an 8-under 64.
